category: Graphics
requires: liblcms2_2 libjpeg-devel libtiff-devel
external-source: lcms2
sdesc: "Little CMS color management library (development)"
ldesc: "Little CMS intends to be a small-footprint color management 
engine, with special focus on accuracy and performance. It uses the 
International Color Consortium standard (ICC), which is the modern 
standard when regarding to color management."
